{
  "description": "Berry is a committed and respected contributor within the Pengu and Abstract community. He consistently engages in discussions, provides thoughtful input, and supports others in a constructive way. His contributions are practical and add real value to the ecosystem.\n\nAs a Lil Pudgy holder, Berry demonstrates long-term conviction and alignment with the project’s vision. He is focused, dependable, and contributes with intent rather than noise."
}

{
